gwt.material.design.client.ui.animate

Class MaterialAnimation

  • java.lang.Object
    • gwt.material.design.client.ui.animate.MaterialAnimation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasDelayTransition, HasDurationTransition

    public class MaterialAnimation
extends Object
implements HasDurationTransition, HasDelayTransition
    Stateful object holding animation details. Default behaviour is a bounce transition for 800ms.
